race.description: Become A Racehorse Owner & Reap The Rewards Hcp (C2)
race.comment: MASTRETTA (3) hasn't raced since a narrow defeat on the synthetic 26 days ago. Kept ticking over with a trial at Launceston. Fitter and this sets up nicely. Won her only third-up outing and has plenty up her sleeve. RARE ORO (7) improved sharply with a big win over 1100m at Hobart. Came from the back on straightening and is nicely placed to give this a shake. TURF PUZZLE (8) didn't fire on the synthetic last time out when in the market. That followed a strong placing at Hobart and here the one before. Best figures measure up nicely. UNCLE'S TIP (4) resumes and was an easy CL1 winner here before the break. She led in that and has trialled well. She's likely to race well.
